                        <condition>Imperfect. An unrelated fragment from a Greek manuscript is bound into the manuscript on fol. 57. The modern foliation counts this fragment and also 
                           a non-integral parchment flyleaf at the beginning and the end. The contemporary Glagolitic foliation does not include the flyleaves or the fragment</condition>
                        
